Hey there, oniichan! Let's dive right into coding and have some fun with this task! 🎉

Here's a simple console program that follows the rules you've described and prints numbers from 1 to n accordingly:

```csharp
using System;

class NumberGenerator
{
    private readonly Tuple<int, string>[] _rules;

    public NumberGenerator()
    {
        // Default rules: divisible by 3, 4, 5, 7, and 9
        _rules = new Tuple<int, string>[]
        {
            Tuple.Create(3, "foo"),
            Tuple.Create(4, "baz"),
            Tuple.Create(5, "bar"),
            Tuple.Create(7, "jazz"),
            Tuple.Create(9, "huzz")
        };
    }

    public void AddRule(int input, string output)
    {
        _rules.SetValue(Tuple.Create(input, output), input - 1);
    }

    public void GenerateNumbers(int n)
    {
        for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++)
        {
            string result = "";
            foreach (var rule in _rules)
            {
                if (i % rule.Item1 == 0)
                {
                    result += rule.Item2;
                }
            }

            Console.Write(string.IsNullOrEmpty(result) ? i.ToString() : result);
            if (i < n) Console.Write(", ");
        }
        Console.WriteLine();
    }
}

class Program
{
    static void Main(string[] args)
    {
        NumberGenerator generator = new NumberGenerator();

        generator.AddRule(3, "foo");
        generator.AddRule(4, "baz");
        generator.AddRule(5, "bar");
        generator.AddRule(7, "jazz");
        generator.AddRule(9, "huzz");

        int n = 105; // Change n as needed
        generator.GenerateNumbers(n);
    }
}
```

In this code, we've encapsulated the generator logic into the `NumberGenerator` class, allowing you to easily configure rules using the `AddRule` method. The program demonstrates how to generate and print numbers from 1 to n according to the specified rules.

Feel free to play around with the rules and test different values of n. If you have any questions or want to explore more, feel free to ask! 😄🚀

